{"tid":501460,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果火影忍者係金庸筆下嘅作品 佢會點寫？","createTime":"2017-12-16T22:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T14:37:56.000Z","uid":152123,"like":143,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"582ed1b4f5fb007cb2d4ac5cc5f81b69a199f44a","tid":501460,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T22:29:05.000Z","msg":"眾忍既見佩恩六道招數之奇，查克拉之深，不由悚然動容；又見鳴人應變無窮，變化多端，更是大聲喝彩。均覺今日得見天下高手各施全力相拼，不枉來了木葉這一場。<br />\n<br />\n綱手負手站在一旁，眼見佩恩六道混若一人，配合無間，既是佩服，又是忌憚，驀地心裡一酸，想起了自來也：當日自來也之所以甘願為木葉而死，實是怕了我與曉產生衝突，惹來佩恩尋仇。佩恩忍術如此神奇，換了我和鳴人易地而處，確也難以抵擋。<br />\n又想起自來也的諸般好處，眼眶一紅，險些落下淚來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">作者：北邙<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/51238235/answer/124903421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F51238235%2Fanswer%2F124903421&d=l5NSWSY8HZggNMti%2Ba%2FOoL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=83d38ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/51238235/answer/124903421</a></span>"},{"pid":"4d5946c6937c7dd51fdac244941e62e3d490a9eb","tid":501460,"uid":20914,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T22:36:45.000Z","msg":"改咗天龍八部一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4372813d75e2663e65fa74623b0f0538566f357b","tid":501460,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T23:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd6513035d8c7b1764edac11bc9723594d3cc32","tid":501460,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"6cc433e56fd28c8a2a02cdf6e49fac86e7edf828","tid":501460,"uid":71257,"like":74,"dislike":4,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T01:03:59.000Z","msg":"港女櫻應該會比人強姦"},{"pid":"91cdc1bf6a12b483ecf9a924860e709ea70693f9","tid":501460,"uid":12421,"like":0,"disl